data.description: Come see this move in ready home! Updated and open floor plan. Stainless steel kitchen appliances, large pantry. Deck off the kitchen, Spacious master bedroom with ensuite. 2nd floor laundry room and Large semi- finished basement with tons of potential. Seller$ credits available. Already is framed and has plumbing. Just needs dry wall.  2 car garage. Ready for a new owner!
